Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:28.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sunday morning kanashimu\Nkoto wa nai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,SAWAGE LIFE Saturday night!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:36.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Omoikkiri hachamecha\Nni ashita wa nichiyoubi!
