Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:46.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,S-A-W-A-G-E Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,S-A-W-A-G-E Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:54.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,SAWAGE LIFE Saturday night!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:57.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sunday morning kanashimu\Nkoto wa nai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:01.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,SAWAGE LIFE Saturday night!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:07.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Omoikkiri hachamecha\Nni ashita wa nichiyoubi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.84,White,,0,0,0,,Què? Ei, ei, ei!\NAlto, que és el meu cotxe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:17.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, que he portat una sospitosa!\NNo s'hi val! Eeeei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.12,White,,0,0,0,,Esperi's! Esperi's! No se l'enduguin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:23.68,White,,0,0,0,,A sobre que ajudo la policia,\Nmira com em tracten! Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:27.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,He-he-he... Sabia que no podíem acabar bé de cap manera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.96,0:22:32.48,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) Caram, és fantàstic!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:35.84,White,,0,0,0,,I què, doctor?\NQuina notícia ens havia de donar?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:38.40,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, ha dit que tenia\Nuna sorpresa per nosaltres.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:42.04,White,,0,0,0,,He pensat fer servir els 10.000 iens d'aquest val que he guanyat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:44.16,White,,0,0,0,,per fer-vos un regal de Nadal\Na cadascú.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:45.64,White,,0,0,0,,(home: crit esfereïdor)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.28,White,,0,0,0,,Caram. Què ha sigut,\Naquest crit tan horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:51.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Venia de les escales!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:54.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No us perdeu el pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:58.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,'Les contradiccions de la Lliga\Nde Detectius Júnior (primera part)'"
